data.value:
Processes define the building blocks of the work item tracking system. When you create a new team project, select the process that matches your enterprise's style of working. Changes made to a process are seen by all team projects that reference it.
 
Team Services provides three system processes, Agile, Scrum and CMMI, based on industry best-practices. To add your own customizations, create an inherited process and update your team project to reference it. An inherited processes adds your customizations to everything inherited from the system process. Learn more
